Vaughan resident says he feared Francesco Villi, condo board fight would ‘end very badly’
By
Ryan Rocca
Global News
Posted December 20, 2022 12:50 pm
Updated December 20, 2022 2:53 pm
6:52
Breaking down the Vaughan mass shooting
Breaking down the Vaughan mass shooting
Deadly mass shooting at condo building rocks Ontario city
